
N = 3
ip = "paradox"
res= ip[:N-1]
print(res)
for i in range(N-1,len(ip)):
    j = ip[i]
    k = ord(j) 
    k = k - ord('a')
    temp = ord('z') - k
    
    #print('ASCII value of {} is {}'.format(i,ord(j)))
    #print(k)
    #print(temp)
    ans = chr(temp)
    res = res + ans
    
    
print(res)


Input : N = 3
        paradox
Output : paizwlc
We mirror characters from position 3 to end.

